# ── Rust / Cargo ──────────────────────────────
# All build output (debug + release) lives here; cargo regenerates it.
/target

# MSVC (your Windows toolchain) writes these debug-symbol files.
# This is almost certainly your "debug files".
*.pdb

# rustfmt backup files, if it ever can't overwrite in place.
**/*.rs.bk

# Cargo.lock stays TRACKED (do not ignore it): this workspace will hold
# binaries, and a committed lockfile keeps their builds reproducible.
# (Library-only crates sometimes ignore it — CERD isn't that.)

# ── Editor / IDE ──────────────────────────────
/.vscode/*
!/.vscode/extensions.json

# ── OS cruft ──────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

# ── Env / secrets ─────────────────────────────
.env
*.local